title: Spain: Catalan farmers rally in the name of independence
description:
Hundreds of farmers rallied in Barcelona, Friday, as Catalonia gears up for the October 1st independence referendum.

SOT, Albert, farmer (Catalan): "Throughout Catalonia there are a lot of people that want what we want and what the government is doing to Catalonia is illogical."

SOT, Jordi, farmer (Catalan): "We came to show our discontent with the fact that they are not letting us vote. Not letting us vote is actually anachronisitic."

SOT, Josep, farmer (Catalan): "We wanted to be seen, because some people cannot see what is happening here. We want to vote, we want freedom of speech and this is our land."
